name: Aegean Boat
description:
Old Greek Gran's NFT #1 - Aegean Boat, Dora Cousoula 2008.

My yiayia still loves painting at the age of 80. All proceeds go to purchasing art supplies for Dora so she can keep finding joy in her craft. Anything over and above goes to paying the bills of the artist and helping her livelihood in her old age.
